{"tid":637132,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人試過係街頭比阿叔撩交打？ 我既處理手法有無問題？","createTime":"2018-04-21T13:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T09:50:09.000Z","uid":33866,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"c6e54ab83b0e3ee6c5af28282c02bac0d05b429b","tid":637132,"uid":33866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩行街，有個阿叔無啦啦屌我<br />\n<br />\n咁我梗係屌柒返佢，跟住佢好似勁嬲咁行埋黎話打柒我定點<br />\n<br />\n屌佢老味咁我當堂梗係都啤實佢，佢行到埋黎痴到實一實<br />\n<br />\n我就即刻開機拍片，話 講多次你頭先講乜，係咪話打柒我話？ 郁我我即刻報警<br />\n<br />\n條撚皮見我部機即刻彈開左口up up左幾句，跟住又走埋黎話叫我del 片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我睇返先發現原來我頭先未禁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (sorry咁多位）<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得遇到呢啲應該點處理？"},{"pid":"4c1fa7fa31a25fb046d81ab2a4b992f8287c760d","tid":637132,"uid":155818,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:52:15.000Z","msg":"拎條巨龍出黎包佢怕怕"},{"pid":"1e36933c03f1130ac5c3ec0d895f9bc307868727","tid":637132,"uid":162539,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"應該走住黎屌"},{"pid":"031316dfbb158f6da85c38b7be34a1de64d035b7","tid":637132,"uid":138355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"即刻跪低認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f05322a40e96412c0372a399a5de71a6e9e9858","tid":637132,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:53:19.000Z","msg":"打你即刻反擊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2baa7ba269e9477cd120d55955fe15677ef38e","tid":637132,"uid":27831,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"含佢碌鳩幫佢出火"},{"pid":"eef7065ec6